ith regional governments, particularly as it relates to policy making aimed at improving the lives of people with intellectual disabilities, is also key.\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"regional governments\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"policy making\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"the lives\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"intellectual disabilities\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said the May 22-26 event hosted at the Lions Community Centre in Grand Cayman underlines the argument that broader support is warranted.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cayman_Islands\", \"score\": 0.9999994862115683, \"rank\": 5.137884745333075e-07, \"text\": \"Grand Cayman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cayman_Islands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cayman_Islands\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the May 22-26 event\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"the Lions Community Centre\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2034}, {\"ngram\": \"the argument\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2074}, {\"ngram\": \"broader support\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Events like these play a crucial role in our efforts by showcasing our athletes and the work we are doing.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Events\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"a crucial role\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"our efforts\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our partners had the opportunity to see firsthand the impact of their contributions, and to get reinforcements about the importance of their support.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our partners\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"their contributions\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"reinforcements\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"their support\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And of course, government involvement is also vital.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"government involvement\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I believe a solid case has been made in favour of the Caribbean Initiative as it seeks to command more resources for regional development,\\\" Bell said.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2478, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\", \"score\": 0.9999999986730472, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caribbean Initiative\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caribbean_Initiative\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a solid case\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"more resources\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"regional development\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"Bell\", \"from\": 2564, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Isaac Rankine, the Cayman Islands Minister of Youth, Sports and Heritage, said his government was proud to have been a major partner in hosting the event.\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2582, \"end\": 2589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Rankine\", \"score\": 0.9970115825050804, \"rank\": 0.0026307258915253774, \"text\": \"Rankine\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Rankine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Rankine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Cayman Islands Minister\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"Youth\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"Heritage\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"his government\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"a major partner\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He, however, added that more can be done.\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the [government's] relationship with Special Olympics Cayman Islands is quite strong, but certainly there is always room for improvement and growth.\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the [government's] relationship\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"Special Olympics Cayman Islands\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"room\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2903}, {\"ngram\": \"improvement\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2919}, {\"ngram\": \"growth\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as long as I am minister of sports I will continue to support it [Special Olympics] and participate whenever and wherever we can,\\\" he told theJamaica Observer.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"minister\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2970}, {\"ngram\": \"Special Olympics\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"theJamaica Observer\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He lauded organisers for staging a world-class event.\",